                                           throws PrismException
        Perform multi-objective model checking computation. Solves achievability, numerical or Pareto queries over n objectives.
        Parameters:
        model - The MDP
        mcLtl - An LTL model checker (for finding end components)
        transRewards - MTBDDs for transition rewards (reward objectives only)
        start - BDD giving the (initial) state for which values are to be computed
        targets - BDDs giving sets of target states (probability objectives only)
        combinations -
        combinationIDs -
        opsAndBounds - Information about the list of objectives
        hasconflictobjectives -
        Throws:
        PrismException
